(65, 'JEB.2019.07.01.005', 251, 'Determinant Factors Influencing the Microfinance Repayment Performance among Amanah Ikhtiar Malaysia?s (AIM?s) Borrower in Jerantut, Pahang', 'determinant factors influencing the microfinance repayment performance among amanah ikhtiar malaysia’s (aim’s) borrower in jerantut, pahang', 'Knowledge, Business Experience, Microfinance', 'Microfinance is one initiative source of financial services for poor?s entrepreneurs that only have small businesses and lacking access to banking and other services. Microfinance always focus to poor people that no steady employment which they cannot even meet the most qualifications to get financial service from normal banking. Thus, the abilities of borrowers in order to pay back their microfinance are one of the arguments that need concentration. This research finding showed that there were only two independent variables which were business experience and loan tenure had significant positive relationship with dependent variable, microfinance repayment performance among AIM?s Borrower in Jerantut, Pahang. However, the knowledge of borrower was no significantly related to the microfinance repayment performance. The result of this study provided the understanding and insight to AIM?s Institution, financial institutions and academic significance to more understanding about how loan giving out and to avoid microfinance repayment defaults.', '', 4, 'ArticleWorkflow/ha-correction', '2019/asrulhery@gmail.com/submission_15583534665ce2963aad4143.68805018.docx', '2019-05-20 20:46:03', '2019-05-20 19:57:33', '2019-05-20 19:58:01', '2019-05-20 20:46:06', 91, 91, '2019/01258A/review_15583563635ce2a18b1fe514.31800992.pdf', '', '2019-05-20 22:43:29', 0, '2019-06-11 14:03:52', 69, '2019-06-11 15:07:41', '\r\n\r\nOverall this article has achieved its objective in identifying the contributing factors towards repayment performance among AIM\'s borrower. The followings are noted and can further be improved:\r\n1. Conceptual framework should be included\r\n2. Normality test and reliability need to be mentioned in data analysis and result section \r\n3. Respondents\' profiling can be tabled out and only highlight the important demographic\r\n4. Sentence structure and grammar need minor revisions so that there is a flow from one sentence to the other.', 4, 4, 'Proceed with accept with minor correction.', 55, '2019-06-12 08:37:46', 69, '2019-06-12 13:15:22', 'Dear Authors\r\n \r\nThis is to inform you that after careful consideration, the editorial team has decided to reconsider for publication should you be prepared to incorporate Minor revisions. When preparing your revised manuscript, you are asked to carefully consider the reviewer comments, which are attached, and submit a list of responses to the comments.\r\n\r\nPlease send the amended version of your paper  by 15th June to consider for JEB June 2019 Issue.\r\n\r\nReviewer\'s Comments:\r\n\r\nOverall this article has achieved its objective in identifying the contributing factors towards repayment performance among AIM\'s borrower. The followings are noted and can further be improved:\r\n1. Conceptual framework should be included\r\n2. Normality test and reliability need to be mentioned in data analysis and result section \r\n3. Respondents\' profiling can be tabled out and only highlight the important demographic', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '', '', 0, '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '');
