(44, 66, 1, 256, 20, 3, 4, 4, 4, 4, 3, 3, 3, 2, 3, 2, 4, '-The Abstract do not firm enough to represent the whole paper, especially about he result.\r\n- No latest issue mentioned in the paper.\r\n-No facts and figures mentioned the paper regarding to banking. \r\n-Rephrase the objective of the paper, unclear.\r\n-Well discussed theory.\r\n-Less mediation discussion focus in the paper, since the paper title stress about the mediation. \r\n-No present of research question, at least main research question should be presented.\r\n-unsatisfied explanation of methodology, most of the discussion pertaining on measurement, in which it could combine all together.\r\n-Since this paper mentioned about the PLS, but no PLS graphic output presented in the paper.\r\n-The result should focus and discuss on mediation.\r\n-A brief of demographic output, reliability and validity should be mentioned. \r\n-Acknowledgement should pertaining your sponsor. \r\n-Inconsistency use of citation.\r\n-Please check grammar and use of word.\r\n', '', '2019-05-30 11:45:55', '2019-05-25 23:11:39', '2019-05-30 13:39:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
