(55, 74, 4, 240, 20, 4, 4, 4, 4, 4, 3, 3, 3, 3, 3, 4, 4, 'Suggestion for Methodology and analysis part.\r\n\r\nInstead of using simple multiple linear regression to determine the the determinant, the Generalize method of moment analysis are suggested. Since the data for one country is greater than 50 ( 9  years x 12 months = 108), GMM method suitable to used. Based on GMM, the authors may test for difference GMM and system GMM. Authors also highly suggested to make robustness test like include time dummy to ensure that the result is not influenced by time specific effects.', '', '2019-06-02 08:03:30', '2019-05-29 08:55:06', '2019-06-02 08:19:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
