(133, 79, 6, 116, 20, 2, 4, 4, 1, 3, 3, 3, 3, 3, 3, 4, 1, 'The topic are good. However,  some major revision are needed.  Author Author need to write comprehensively especially on their problem statement, LR.', '', '2019-10-31 18:15:21', '2019-10-28 21:14:11', '2019-10-31 18:25:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(134, 79, 6, 138, 20, 3, 4, 4, 3, 2, 3, 4, 3, 3, 1, 4, 3, 'This is an interesting study and the authors have collected some interesting data using quantitative methodology.  The paper is generally well written and structured. However, in my opinion the paper has some shortcomings in regards to formatting, structure and analysis which need to be rectified.  ', '', '2019-11-01 09:26:52', '2019-10-28 21:14:11', '2019-11-01 09:51:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
