(29, 159, 0, '', 'This course will discuss on the method that will be used to improve productivity through the development and industry management quality system enhancement. The discussion will include the knowledge of management, raw materials, safety and equipment (plant system). Apart from the logistics aspect, human resource management, innovation and technology transfer also will be discussed throughout this course. ', '', '', '1. Penilaian Berterusan.\r\n2. Peperiksaan Akhir.', '1. Continuous Assessment.\r\n2. Final Examination.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(30, 160, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(31, 161, 0, 'Kursus ini membekalkan pelajar pengetahuan asas berkaitan dengan proses huluan ( penemuan dan penciptaan), proses hiliran (penulenan dan pemecilan), pengujian ketulenan dan kestabilan agen biofarmaseutikal. Agen biofarmaseutikal dibincangkan secara khusus mengikut kelas kegunaannya. Kursus ini juga menerangkan keperluan keselamatan dan keberkesanan mengikut peraturan dan standard antarabangsa.', 'This course provides the students with the basic knowledge regarding upstream processing (discovery and invention), downstream processing \'(purification and isolation), purity and stability testing of biopharmaceutical agents. Biopharmaceutical agents is discussed specifically by it applications. This course also explains the safety and efficacy requirements in accordance to international standards and regulations.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
