(35, 165, 0, '', 'This course discuss on principles of tissue, cell and organ culture from plant origin, including factors that influence the maintainance of cells for their growth and development. Besides this, the course also focus on the components of tissue culture such as media composition, media pH, temperature, shaking and aeration rates of cultures. The goal of tissue culture technology course is to enrich the knowledge among the students to improve the production of artificial seeds, new hybrids, cross-breeding and production of secondary metabolite that is plant active substances, vaccines, antibodies and monoclones through tissue and cell culture technique.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(36, 166, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(37, 167, 0, 'Kursus ini bertujuan untuk memperkenalkan proses dan mekanisma pemisahan yang biasa digunakan di industri. Pelajar akan diperkenalkan kepada reka bentuk proses pemisahan berdasarkan konsep peringkat keseimbangan dan konsep kadar pemindahan jisim untuk penyulingan, penyerapan, dan ekstraksi cecair-cecair. Kaedah pendek untuk sistem multikomponen akan diterangkan. Pengenalan kepada proses membran dan penjerapan untuk pemisahan gas akan diberikan. ', 'The course aims to introduce the process and mechanism of separation is commonly used in industry. Students will be introduced to the design concept stage separation process based on the concept of equilibrium and mass transfer rate for distillation, absorption, and liquid-liquid extraction. Short methods for multicomponent system will be described. Introduction to the membrane and adsorption processes for gas separation will be provided.', '', 'separation techniques ', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
